<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><meta charset="utf-8"><title>Listing Approved</title></head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <h1 style="color: #16a34a;">Congratulations! Your Listing is Live</h1>
  <p>Hi {{recipientName}},</p>
  <p>Great news! Your business listing <strong>{{businessName}}</strong> has been approved and is now visible in the Digital Directory.</p>
  <p>Potential customers can now discover your business through search and browsing.</p>
  {{#if listingUrl}}
  <p>
    <a href="{{listingUrl}}"
       style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #16a34a; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px;">
      View Your Listing
    </a>
  </p>
  {{/if}}
  <p>To manage your listing, log in to your dashboard and navigate to your business profile.</p>
  <p>Best regards,<br>The Digital Directory Team</p>
</body>
</html>
